name: Memento Mauri #13
description: A most peculiar Soul, found wandering the Undercroft of Animus by the Founder of the Smiling Shinigami. A frail figure starving and nearly feral; Her face seemed disfigured over years of fighting and survival. To compensate for her size, the Smiling Shinigami outfitted her with Selket's Kiss, a unique Bio-Mech Augment stemming from #13's Shoulder Blades. Selket's Kiss contains an ever potent paralysis poison within the left Stinger, and a Neurotoxin capable of sending foes into a Frenzy in the right dosages. #13 doesn't seem to age, remaining in Combat Ready state long after the Founder had passed, retaining her Rank along the way.
